<br />

<br />
One comment I'll make to you is, unless you just happen to have gotten all those items, why would you seek some of them out (outside the 2.0 singing one) if you were so close to your epic. Said another way, why would you give up the UBER items that you COULD be getting for the slots you are putting your instruments in, just so you could find a better weapon when we aren't tanks per se.  Don't get me wrong, I like to mix it up with mobs when I'm not getting hit, but if I do 80 damage once in a blue moon rather than 60 that I can do now, so what, when the tank just crit for 10,000?  hehe get my point?
